law.text: Airport development in Kentucky may be undertaken and paid for by the state, the United States and governmental units. Costs for development may be borne by any one (1) of these or by any combination.
law.history: Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 274, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 18. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 179, sec. 69. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 6.
